On Whonix-Gateway.

For explanation, open {{Code|/etc/whonix_firewall.d/30_user}} and read what the settings GATEWAY_TRANSPARENT_TCP and GATEWAY_TRANSPARENT_DNS are about.

<pre>
kwrite /etc/whonix_firewall.d/30_user
</pre>

Create a file {{Code|/etc/whonix_firewall.d/50_user}}.

<pre>
kdesudo kwrite /etc/whonix_firewall.d/50_user
</pre>

Add the following content.

</pre>
GATEWAY_TRANSPARENT_TCP=1
GATEWAY_TRANSPARENT_DNS=1
</pre>

Save.

Reload Wohnix's Firewall.

<pre>
sudo whonix_firewall
</pre>

Open {{Code|/etc/tor/torrc}}.

<pre>
kdesudo kwrite /etc/tor/torrc
</pre>

Add the following content.

<pre>
TransPort 127.0.0.1:9041
DnsPort 127.0.0.1:54
</pre>

Reload Tor.

<pre>
sudo service tor reload
</pre>

Test if you wish.

<pre>
curl.whonix-orig https://check.torproject.org
</pre>

